short_description: blue river cabinetry is a cabinet maker based in fredericksburg, indiana, united states.
long_description: blue river cabinetry stands on a solid foundation of more than its amish roots. we continue to be committed to providing superior handcrafted cabinets, while ensuring service is nothing less than exceptional. at blue river we understand the value of work well done - every piece is built to endure, inside and out. specialty features and design options are virtually unlimited. and, attention to detail is what we do best. whether you are looking for exquisite custom cabinets, an entertainment center, a bathroom vanity or other fine custom cabinetry work, blue river cabinetry will work to provide the beauty and custom features that you desire. our goal is to be the regions first and last choice for superior cabinetry.
